\b Forests of Old [Galadriel]:\par
\b0\par
objectives:\par
1. Search for magic and Dwarven rings, and get Treebeard and Tom together\par
2. Move to Mount Doom to Raid the cracks of doom.\par
hazards: Elves and Awakened Plants\par
play tips:\par
starting company: Thranduil (Thrall of the Voice, Bow of Yew), Celeborn Lord of Lorien (Trusted Counsellor), Wood-elf (Elven Rope)\par
- your starting company will play gold rings and Essays. These you can test with Ringlore or Wizard's Test (sideboard, use with Ancient Skill), or store them.\par
- once you get Treebeard in play, sideboard Tom Bombadil in; you can move to Tom's House using A Long Good Talk. If you cannot start Thranduil, Galadriel will have to get moving, otherwise she stays at L\'f3rien.\par
- tap Galadriel to get Leaf Brooch, Waybread, Cup of Farewell and Nenya to the discard. Use Galadriel and Lady of Many Gifts to play them\par
- nearing the end of your cycle, sideboard Tower Raided in. Move to Mount Doom (using Waybread), where you can invert Into the Smoking Cone, which you can store with Long Good Talk\par
- with a Dwarven Ring on Galadriel you can play The Elf-king\par
